author: Jasmine
content:
I try the dress once I receive it and I'm very happy with it. I'm more impressed with the pants. Usually the pants that come with these kurta sets will be ankle length or short and a bit tight around the thighs. But this one is long enough and perfect so I can move around comfortably. And the real bang is it has a pocket; not a tiny namesake one but an actual pocket like you can keep your mobile phone in.
Loved it
